the adventures of hercules ( italian : le avventure dell ' incredibile ercole ) , also known as hercules ii , is the 1985 sequel to the 1983 film hercules . it was written and directed by luigi cozzi ( credited as lewis coates in the american release ) who also directed the previous film , and had lou ferrigno reprising his role as the title character . pino donaggio 's music for the first film is reused here in lieu of an original score .